snippet.title: Trick & Treat: Trailer
snippet.description:
A small horror/puzzle game. 
Free on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/497640
By RbbitonBooks, 2016

Original music: "Halloween" by Zephysonas
https://m.youtube.com/user/Zephysonas
https://zephysonas.bandcamp.com

The game will be released on Steam soon.
RMN: https://rpgmaker.net/games/8667/
Itch: https://rabooks.itch.io/trickandtreat
